{"tid":2075744,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傳美斯基斯文操練炒大鑊","createTime":"2020-06-23T05:02:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T16:43:59.000Z","uid":72497,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"a37e194ab3a5443bc99c21e48815a59b7fb96042","tid":2075744,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:02:15.000Z","msg":"巴塞隆拿今季不時傳出內亂，最近就有指美斯、基斯文在操練中發生衝突。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙《Diario Gol》爆料，美斯（Lionel Messi）與基斯文（Antoine Griezmann）日前在操練中發生衝突，而且火爆程度令所有注視，令教練錫迪安不得不介入，分開兩人。 據知基斯文今季以1.2億歐元從馬德里體育會加盟巴塞隆拿後，一直未能踢出身價，令作為老大哥的美斯相當不滿，早前對利根尼斯的西甲已經故意不傳球予基斯文。 <br />\n<br />\n另外，根據西班牙《世界體育報》指，美斯正跟巴塞商討續約。在新型冠狀病毒疫情影響球會財政下，美斯同意在這份2年的新約將不會獲得加薪。"},{"pid":"2d9fcf951c0085fd066d6e80d30de3c788901074","tid":2075744,"uid":14075,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:04:03.000Z","msg":"球霸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e64791b3b2454b5685c3df2e75a95a5d3a00a8","tid":2075744,"uid":72497,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"2d9fcf951c0085fd066d6e80d30de3c788901074","tid":2075744,"uid":14075,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:04:03.000Z","msg":"球霸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:04:17.000Z","msg":"愛之深責之切"},{"pid":"56a9c1fc1c986c02fd67e3426854f21b3528eb8b","tid":2075744,"uid":2949,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:04:33.000Z","msg":"往死裏打"},{"pid":"0d2f230d48868ec21cdb4ee5508be7257e0c623a","tid":2075744,"uid":191926,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:07:01.000Z","msg":"美斯接班人=習近平接班人<br />\n<br />\n個個都非死即傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e356f65b6e075154453f3b7daef53731b2322dd","tid":2075744,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:08:27.000Z","msg":"基斯文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /